Braun and beauty vlogger Becca Rose have come together to introduce you to the Braun facial Bonus Pack for the Braun 2 in 1 Face device. The bonus pack contains 4 changeable heads; the normal brush to cleanse 6x better than manual wash, the exfoliation brush to sweep away dead skin, the extra sensitive brush to gently cleanse dry and sensitive skin and the beauty sponge to apply evenly make-up. This pack allows you to tailor your skincare routine to all of your beauty needs. Break free from impurities with the Braun Face!
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                
To learn more about the Braun products that Becca Rose has recommended for getting your skin moisturised and glowing, check out http://www.braun.com/global/female-grooming/braun-face.html and http://www.braun.com/global for more beauty and lifestyle products that make a difference!
